Package lombok.core Description

Contains the platform-agnostic core of lombok. Includes the lombok AST superclasses, annotation introspection support, an implementation of SPI service loader (to avoid being dependent on a v1.6 JVM), lombok's version, and annotations and support classes for your normal java code that's primarily useful for developing and debugging lombok. NB: This package is not public API in the sense that contents of this package, even public classes / methods / etc, may change in point releases.
